125 years memory ( 海難1890 kainan 1890 ) is a 2015 drama film directed by mitsutoshi tanaka and written by eriko komatsu . a japanese-turkish co-production , the film was released in japan by toei on december 5 , 2015 and in turkey by mars on december 25 , 2015 . it received ten nominations at the 39th japan academy prize , winning the awards for best art direction and best sound recording .